trans-unit.source: Represents the collection of <xref uid="langword_csharp_<identityConfiguration>" name="<identityConfiguration>" href=""></xref> elements in a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: 表示的集合<xref uid="langword_csharp_<identityConfiguration>" name="<identityConfiguration>" href=""></xref>配置文件中的元素。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
A configuration file can have multiple `<identityConfiguration>` elements.
trans-unit.target: 配置文件可以有多个`<identityConfiguration>`元素。

trans-unit.source: Each identity configuration is identified by a unique name specified in its `name` attribute.
trans-unit.target: 由中指定唯一名称标识每个标识配置其`name`属性。

trans-unit.source: Each `<identityConfiguration>` element is represented by an <xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IdentityConfigurationElement> object.
The [Name](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) property of each object contains the name of the identity configuration.
trans-unit.target: [名称](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)每个对象的属性包含标识配置的名称。

trans-unit.source: The IdentityConfigurationElementCollection class wraps a collection that contains all of the `<identityConfiguration>` elements read from the file.
trans-unit.target: IdentityConfigurationElementCollection 类将包装一个集合包含的所有`<identityConfiguration>`元素从文件中读取。

trans-unit.source: The name of the identity configuration is used as a key to retrieve the corresponding <xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IdentityConfigurationElement> when you call the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IdentityConfigurationElementCollection.GetElement%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 标识配置的名称用作密钥用来检索相应<xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IdentityConfigurationElement>当调用<xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IdentityConfigurationElementCollection.GetElement%2A>方法。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IdentityConfigurationElementCollection.GetElement%2A> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IdentityConfigurationElement>
